<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/heritage/library/categories/crimelaw/bg1057.html 204.71.237.86 19970108141044 text/html 39282
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 14:11:00 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 19-Mar-96 22:34:43 GMT
